=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/590f996ca1c8b32cddeff87b5a5659eb.avif?t=1715806965\" width=616 height=386 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/ddaf06e658f0aac161511e8e4aaa32cc.poster.avif?t=1715806965\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/ddaf06e658f0aac161511e8e4aaa32cc.webm?t=1715806965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/ddaf06e658f0aac161511e8e4aaa32cc.mp4?t=1715806965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/7bd6c559a2a45781cf0b22ad8f347e3d.poster.avif?t=1715806965\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/7bd6c559a2a45781cf0b22ad8f347e3d.webm?t=1715806965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/7bd6c559a2a45781cf0b22ad8f347e3d.mp4?t=1715806965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/b0a36ab3ba2bec96ca7170146d918414.avif?t=1715806965\" width=618 height=386 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1436920/extras/edcf78c604a09e38f0ce080c66ad6b5c.poster.avif?t=1715806965\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite